<br>
But we will <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>not</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> cooperate. Our blood will not be diluted by the filth that preaches love and peace. In shadows and darkness we grow - ever training, ever scheming. <br>
<br>
Many have set out on this path, and many have faltered. Others claim that our way of life is but a thing of the past, that we shall fade away into memory. And yet, I find that we are still strong. As long as a few remain with the strength to do so, we shall war. <br>
<br>
The decision here is yours to make: shall you war beside us or against us?<br>
<br>
--<br>
<br>
OOC: For those that might not know, we are an evil roleplaying guild. We're quite strict about who we allow into the guild - we are an army, and as such we must insure that we can trust those that we extend an invitation to. Of course anyone that meets the requirements can, and is encouraged to apply. I promise we don't bite.<br>
<br>
To see the requirements and what we're about, our charter is here: <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://pub99.ezboard.com/fmalevolentdesiresfrm14.showMessage?topicID=4.topic">pub99.ezboard.com/fmalevo...ID=4.topic</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
<br>
At the moment we're getting back into fairly regular practices in the arena. You can also be sure that if there are any in your level range, you'll have someone to hunt with.<br>
<br>
We have one of our little arena practices planned for the very near future, so if you'd like to join and get to know us a bit, do let me know and I'll give you the details.<br>
<br>
